Cook bacon in 10-inch skillet over medium heat until crisp. Transfer bacon with a slotted spoon to a paper towel; set aside. Cook onion in drippings in skillet until tender, about 5 minutes, stirring occasionally. Stir in BUSH'S BEST Blackeye Peas and tomatoes; simmer uncovered 5 minutes, stirring occasionally. Top with reserved bacon and serve warm.